data.description: This wonderful home is in the Pueblo West Golf Course area and offers 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an attached 2 car garage and 2 sheds. The upper level consists of the master bedroom with an attached bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms, as well as an additional bathroom. On the main level you will find the kitchen, dining room and the living room. Head down to the lower level to a nice sized family room big enough to entertain all of your friends and family. Down in the basement you will find another bedroom and bathroom, as well as the laundry room. Relax outside with a huge enclosed patio and enjoy your view of the mountains. Ample parking with a concrete pad for your RV or Boat. Save on energy costs with a tankless water heater as well as solar panels. Now this is a place you can call home.
